{
  "stem": "17626.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it wasn't until the treaty-- I think it was in 1941 but I'm not quite sure of my history dates-- that the Russian and Polish governments had a treaty that the Polish citizens residing in Russia from the time that they were evacuated from the time of the war in 1939 were allowed to leave that area and settle in other cities in Russia, either the capital provincial cities.",
      "word_count": 70
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we were in Archangel [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] 14 or 17 months during which time my father-- and we were as prisoners there because you couldn't go, you couldn't leave the place.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "First of all, where it was and secondly, if you left, you had to have transportation.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You couldn't-- either you went into the ocean or you went into the forest.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Neither one of them gave you a very good choice because if you didn't have transportation, you were lost.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I don't, especially not from the Jewish community that was there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Originally there was a prison, and it was a Russian prison of many years in existence.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we were sort of the addition to that-- to that area.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I couldn't tell you, but there must have been at least 10, 14 Villages.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they were called a [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And each [INAUDIBLE] had a number, rather than a name.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] number one, [INAUDIBLE] number two.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "After the war, we met a lot of people who were [INAUDIBLE] number six, [INAUDIBLE] 23, [INAUDIBLE] 14, you know.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Number one.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's where my mother-- there was a hospital there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My mother worked in the hospital.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My father worked with the horses.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was grazing the horses at night.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
